<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Registro de Nuevo Cliente</title>

    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.css" />
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/cropperjs/1.5.13/cropper.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/img/favicon-16x16.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <meta name="csrf-token" content="<%= csrfToken %>">

    <style>
        :root {
            --font-main: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            --primary: #0d6efd;
            --primary-light: #e7f1ff;
            --bg-body: #f3f5f9;
            --text-dark: #1e293b;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
            --border-color: #e2e8f0;
            --card-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.025);
        }

        body {
            font-family: var(--font-main);
            background-color: var(--bg-body);
            color: var(--text-dark);
        }

        /* --- Header & Navigation --- */
        .btn-back {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            background: white;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .btn-back:hover {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: var(--text-dark);
            border-color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        /* --- Main Card --- */
        .content-card {
            background-color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* --- Wizard / Progress Steps --- */
        .wizard-container {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            padding: 0 1rem;
        }

        .progress-line-bg {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 50px;
            right: 50px;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            z-index: 1;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .progress-line-fill {
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 50px;
            height: 4px;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            z-index: 2;
            border-radius: 2px;
            transition: width 0.4s ease;
            width: 0%;
        }

        .steps-wrapper {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 3;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 2rem;
            /* Ajuste para centrar mejor */
        }

        .step-item {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            width: 100px;
            /* Ancho fijo para centrar texto */
        }

        .step-circle {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: white;
            border: 2px solid #cbd5e1;
            color: #64748b;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .step-label {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #94a3b8;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        /* Active State */
        .step-item.active .step-circle {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--primary-light);
        }

        .step-item.active .step-label {
            color: var(--text-dark);
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* --- Form Inputs --- */
        .form-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #334155;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .form-control {
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            border: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.15);
        }

        .form-text {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-top: 0.4rem;
        }

        /* --- File Upload --- */
        .drop-zone {
            border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        .drop-zone:hover,
        .drop-zone.dragover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            background-color: var(--primary-light);
        }

        .drop-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .drop-zone:hover .drop-icon {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* --- Cropper --- */
        #cropper-container {
            background-color: #f1f5f9;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* --- Info Panel (Sidebar) --- */
        .info-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }

        .info-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .info-item {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .info-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .info-icon-wrapper {
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background-color: var(--primary-light);
            color: var(--primary);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* --- Buttons --- */
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: var(--primary);
            border: none;
            padding: 0.6rem 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.2);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #0b5ed7;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(13, 110, 253, 0.3);
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row mb-4 align-items-end">
            <div class="col">
                <h1 class="h3 mb-1 text-dark fw-bold">Registro de Nuevo Cliente</h1>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Configura los datos esenciales de la empresa.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-auto">
                <a href="/admin/visualizar_empresas" class="btn-back">
                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-left"></i> Volver
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="content-card p-4 p-lg-5">

                    <div class="wizard-container">
                        <div class="progress-line-bg"></div>
                        <div class="progress-line-fill" id="progress-line"></div>

                        <div class="steps-wrapper">
                            <div class="step-item active" id="step-indicator-1">
                                <div class="step-circle">1</div>
                                <span class="step-label">Información</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="step-item" id="step-indicator-2">
                                <div class="step-circle">2</div>
                                <span class="step-label">Logo</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="alert-placeholder" class="mb-4"></div>

                    <form id="empresa-form" novalidate>

                        <div class="form-step active" data-step="1">
                            <div class="mb-4 pb-2 border-bottom">
                                <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark">Datos Generales</h5>
                            </div>

                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <label for="nombre" class="form-label">Nombre de la Empresa <span
                                        class="text-danger">*</span></label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control form-control-lg" id="nombre"
                                    placeholder="Ej: Acme Corporation" required maxlength="150">
                            </div>

                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <label for="direccion" class="form-label">Dirección Fiscal <span
                                        class="text-danger">*</span></label>
                                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="direccion"
                                    placeholder="Ej: Av. Principal 123, Lima" required maxlength="255">
                            </div>

                            <div class="mb-4">
                                <label for="slug" class="form-label">URL de Acceso (Slug) <span
                                        class="text-danger">*</span></label>
                                <div class="input-group">
                                    <span class="input-group-text bg-light text-muted">/</span>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="slug" placeholder="acme-corp" required
                                        maxlength="50">
                                </div>
                                <div class="form-text">Este identificador único se usará en la URL del portal del
                                    cliente.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-step" data-step="2" style="display: none;">
                            <div class="mb-4 pb-2 border-bottom">
                                <h5 class="fw-bold text-dark">Identidad Visual</h5>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-muted mb-4">Sube el logotipo oficial. Se recomienda una imagen cuadrada (PNG
                                o JPG) de al menos 400x400px.</p>

                            <input type="file" id="logo" accept="image/png, image/jpeg" required style="display: none;">

                            <div id="drop-zone" class="drop-zone">
                                <div id="drop-zone-prompt">
                                    <i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-up drop-icon"></i>
                                    <h6 class="fw-bold text-dark">Haz clic o arrastra tu imagen aquí</h6>
                                    <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Soporta PNG y JPG (Máx 5MB)</p>
                                </div>

                                <div id="cropper-container" class="d-none" style="height: 400px;">
                                    <img src="" alt="Vista previa" id="logo-preview">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-between mt-5 pt-3 border-top">
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-light text-muted px-4" id="btn-prev"
                                style="display: none;">
                                <i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-2"></i> Anterior
                            </button>

                            <div class="ms-auto"> <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary px-4" id="btn-next">
                                    Siguiente <i class="bi bi-arrow-right ms-2"></i>
                                </button>
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success px-4 text-white" id="btn-submit"
                                    style="display: none;">
                                    <i class="bi bi-check2-circle me-2"></i> Guardar Empresa
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <div class="info-card position-sticky" style="top: 2rem;">
                    <h6 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4">Guía Rápida</h6>

                    <ul class="info-list">
                        <li class="info-item">
                            <div class="info-icon-wrapper">
                                <i class="bi bi-building-check"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <strong class="d-block text-dark mb-1">Nombre Exacto</strong>
                                <span class="text-muted small">Usa el nombre comercial o razón social tal como aparecerá
                                    en los reportes.</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="info-item">
                            <div class="info-icon-wrapper">
                                <i class="bi bi-link-45deg"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <strong class="d-block text-dark mb-1">URL Amigable</strong>
                                <span class="text-muted small">El "Slug" debe ser corto y sin espacios. Se genera
                                    automático pero puedes editarlo.</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                        <li class="info-item">
                            <div class="info-icon-wrapper">
                                <i class="bi bi-crop"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <strong class="d-block text-dark mb-1">Recorte de Logo</strong>
                                <span class="text-muted small">Usa la herramienta de recorte en el paso 2 para centrar
                                    perfectamente la marca.</span>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/cropperjs/1.5.13/cropper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/formularioempresa.js"></script>

</body>

</html>